==English==
===Noun===
'''pistol''' (Plural '''pistols''')

# A [[handgun]], typically with a semi-automatic action and a clip magazine.

====Related terms====
*[[machine pistol]]

====Translations====
*Dutch: [[pistool]] {{n}}
*Finnish: [[pistooli]]

====Usage note====
Shooters normally differentiate between a pistol and a [[revolver]], however, in common usage, the word ''pistol'' is used to refer to any type of [[handgun]].

